There&#39;s some restrictions when doing sql injection, for example the sanitize_string function will limit your input with 39 character, and the spectial character like &amp;quot;;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;/&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;|&amp;quot; will be replaced with &amp;quot;&amp;quot;. However, I can still bypass these restrictions and get rce with load_extension and evil-so file.&lt;br /&gt;
With the sqlite injection, we can input&lt;/p&gt;
